code: @Override public boolean isCreateCamelContextPerClass() {     // only create the context once for this class     return true. }

@SuppressWarnings("unchecked") protected <T> T requestBodyAndHeaders(String endpointUri, Object body, Map<String, Object> headers) throws CamelExecutionException {     return (T) template().requestBodyAndHeaders(endpointUri, body, headers). }
